title: Whole Foods Christmas Tree Adventure
body:
Me: Looking at Christmas trees outside

Random Group of Girls to Each Other: Didn’t @taylorswift grow-up on a Christmas tree farm? 

Me: Well yeah! Until she moved to Nashville to become the legend that she is today! 

Random Group of Girls: That is amazing that you know that! 

Me: Oh, I thought that was common knowledge. 

**Exits with tiny Christmas tree for myself**

Always love TS facts!
